title: Genasi of Earth
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki
xpcost: 1

As an earth [[genasi]], you gain the following benefits.

* You have [[tremorsense]] out to 10 feet.
* You can move across uneven terrain made of stone or earth without slowing your pace.
* You can cast one of the following spells: [[pass without trace]], [[mold earth]], [[earth tremor]], [[earthen grasp]], or [[mending]].
